commit_message: Updates apigenome to fix malformed headers and EXHET filter.
Updates cramore to use AD instead of DP for setting GT to missing.
Updates cramore to fix corrupted INFO fields.
Updates cramore and fixes squeeze regions in Snakefile.
Expects htslib executables to be in $PATH.
Adds new fields to update sites script.
Removes extra "chr" prefix in GWAS catalog whitelist script.
Adds hard filter script that supports chrX and fixes duplicated chr prefix.
Sets bcftools and samtools to v1.9.
Switches build order of cramore and vt-topmed since cramore links dynamically.
Uses htslib v1.9 for vt-topmed to fix faidx_fetch_uc_seq issue (cramore requires v1.10 or greater).
Updates compilation of new libsvm in singularity image.
Updates cramore to include IO error handling.
Updates cramore to include male-X specific depth filter.
Updates version of vt-topmed to fix build error with new version of htslib.
Updates cramore and apigenome to reflect freeze 9 changes.
Fixes plink install in singularity image and stops errors from being ignored.
Quick fix for static curl lib issue.
Includes fix for ignoring missing cram index.
Updates singularity definition to support cramore with cmake.
Updates cramore version to fix silent IO errors.
Updated cramore package to fix bug
Updates plink binary name in singularity image.
More fixes on vt-topmed compile error on abs()
Added vt-topmed module, which was missing by mistake before
Reorganized the contents to have submodules with comprehensive examples
